data.title: The Credit Union for Washington: Join Us Today
data.meta_description: We're a member-powered credit union that focuses on you and the communities that make Washington such an amazing place to call home.
data.text:
Buying a new home is an adventure. It can also be stressful, especially in today’s housing market. But that’s why we’re here. We’ll guide you along the way to help make your new home purchase as easy as possible.

Learn more

Life is full of surprises. Whether you have an unexpected expense, need to consolidate debt or want to take a vacation, WSECU can help. Apply online for a personal loan or line of credit and use the funds however you need.

Learn more

If you’re a Washington driver, auto insurance is essential to help protect you from the costs of an accident. It’s also required by Washington state law and most auto financing lenders. Let us help get you covered.*

Learn more

When the unexpected happens, Q-Cash is there for you by providing access to short-term funds, day or night. Complete a simple application process (six clicks in 60 seconds) and, if approved, the funds get immediately deposited into your account. No credit report necessary — all you need is a smartphone or computer.

Learn more
